    <p>I mean, that's the other thing is, like, doing this and talking to women or men who have - who are suffering from chronic pain on a daily basis, it is so unimaginable. I mean, I was so grateful for my body at the end of the day. You know what I mean?</p>
    <p>MARTIN: Little things we take for granted.</p>
    <p>ANISTON: The little - exactly. Exactly.</p>
