    <p>OVERBY: But, he says, if you don't bring good, reliable information...</p>
    <p>BENNETT: Your axis doesn't do you any good at all.</p>
    <p>OVERBY: It's all a matter of finding where the lawmakers' goals match those of your client - in other words, same as it ever was. Peter Overby, NPR News, Washington.</p>
