    <p>(SOUNDBITE OF MUSIC)</p>
    <p>JOHN OTIS, BYLINE: Shortly before taking the stage at a Quito bar, the Ecuadorian band Samay Blues plugs in for a sound check.</p>
    <p>(SOUNDBITE OF MUSIC)</p>
    <p>OTIS: Some of the bar-goers tonight are Americans. That's because the word is out. U.S. Ambassador Adam Namm will be sitting in on keyboards.</p>
