    <p>SIMON: I don't hear a dog in the background, though.</p>
    <p>KRALL: Yes, well, in the original - in the bootleg I believe there is a dog barking and it's a bit of a broken piano and I can imagine afternoons being played on the piano and just playing it. That was in my thoughts of how warm it felt.</p>
